{"word":"ἐπιψεύδομαι","slug":"ἐπιψεύδομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιψεύδομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to lie still more</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to attribute falsehood to</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to falsify</i> a number, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}